      "username": "Br3dharaku",
      "name": "Br3dh, br3dho...",
      "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/peshkupauje.com/br3dharaku/{size}/6132_2.png",
      "created_at": "2017-08-08T20:08:35.819Z",
      "cooked": "<p>kjo eshte seri me pulla kushtuar vendeve evropiane<br>\n<img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/2X/5/5fca2d6ab996ce8539143103fa630d2a5310d095.jpg\" alt=\"fr\" width=\"340\" height=\"270\"><img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/2X/4/4b9c54dfefa8d27ba2eca8d31c3828effc3fd4a0.jpg\" alt=\"nor\" width=\"537\" height=\"355\"><img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/2X/6/654b1e3080af6da337c8951abacb18f3956dbce5.jpg\" alt=\"lux\" width=\"629\" height=\"408\"><br>\n<img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/2X/e/e3bb69ed21ecb4504481ce6a6a03786b1b79b5ec.jpg\" alt=\"aus\" width=\"484\" height=\"320\"><img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/2X/f/fa4d36d819ec12fd34eaed482b00e768b90175c4.jpg\" alt=\"cs\" width=\"614\" height=\"410\"></p>",
      "reply_to_post_number": null,
      "like_count": 0
    },
    {
      "id": 46385,
      "post_number": 5,
      "username": "Kthupi",
      "name": "",
      "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/k/3bc359/{size}.png",
      "created_at": "2017-08-08T20:17:38.861Z",
      "cooked": "<p>FDR ishte Jon Voight megjithese i kishin bere cik saldim fytyres e s’dallohej dhe aq kollaj. Alec Baldwin, not Alex you freakin’ immigrant. <img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/images/emoji/apple/smile.png?v=5\" title=\":smile:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":smile:\"></p>\n<p>Ama shife propaganden amerikane. Jo me kot emetimi 5 cent ishte ai ku u krijuan keto pulla. 5 cent ishte international mail, i merrnin letrat ushtaret ne Evrope. Ne anen e majte feniksi domethene ringritja e ketyre vendeve, ne anen e djathte nje grua qe ka thyer zinxhiret. Not expressly stated, por nenkuptimi eshte qe Amerika e ka mendjen tek ju dhe vetem prej Amerikes do thyeni zinxhiret e do ringriheni si feniksi. U tha u be, per 2 vjet e cliroi Evropen. Jo, fol po deshe.</p>",
      "reply_to_post_number": 3,
      "like_count": 0
    },
    {
      "id": 46386,
      "post_number": 6,
      "username": "anon64581289",
      "name": "",
      "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/a/3ab097/{size}.png",
      "created_at": "2017-08-08T20:18:31.986Z",
      "cooked": "<p>partizonet me enverin s’duhet te kene pasur dijeni per kete dashurine amerikane te sinqerte ndaj popullit tone heroik, se te paret qe hoqen prej shqiperise qene amerikont.</p>",
      "reply_to_post_number": null,
      "like_count": 0
    },
    {
      "id": 46387,
