      "name": "",
      "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/k/3bc359/{size}.png",
      "created_at": "2017-08-08T20:22:03.962Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Enveri ju lut amerikaneve per ndihme se ndiqte shembullin e Titos. Amerikanet kishin oficere te OSS te atashuar ne forcat partizane qe bashkerendonin veprimet me aleatet.</p>",
